FBIS3-50710 "drlat004_c_94015" FBIS-LAT-94-004 Document Type:Daily Report 6 Jan 1994 MEXICO Chiapas Crisis Clashes Continue in Ocosingo PA0601012894 Mexico City Radio ACIR Network in Spanish 0030 GMT 6 Jan 94 PA0601012894 Mexico City Radio ACIR Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [From the "Vector 21" newscast] [Text] Clashes are continuing in the area of Ocosingo, Chiapas. As a result, the Mexican Army has restricted access to that municipal capital. During the clashes, rebel gunfire hit a Mexican Air Force helicopter, causing mechanical failure.
